source.name: Degrees and Other Formal Awards Granted by SUNY (includes CUNY 1949-1975): Beginning 1949
source.description: This dataset records the number of degrees and formal awards granted by the State University of New York; it includes degrees awarded by community colleges sponsored by the NYC Board of Higher Education until July 1, 1975.
